{"tid":2429471,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"德國商業銀行退出香港市場","createTime":"2021-03-02T10:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T10:25:08.000Z","uid":259520,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6c96a287a2d9dcee7e62d8d4157353472f816ac5","tid":2429471,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T10:25:08.000Z","msg":"德國商業銀行退出香港市場<br />\n<br />\n有人會話佢撤左好多城市,有咩野出奇.<br />\n問題係香港係幾大國際金融市場之一.<br />\n會無投資價值?? 中德關係唔係太差??<br />\n明顯德國商業銀行都收到D風. 走佬為上.<br />\n<br />\nD5毛成日話香港搵錢易.仲可以繼續搵錢唔好走.<br />\n連德國商業銀行都話走,香港仲邊有運行.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/usstock/c/2021-03-01/doc-ikftpnnz0347473.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.com.cn%2Fstock%2Fusstock%2Fc%2F2021-03-01%2Fdoc-ikftpnnz0347473.shtml&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=a5b4e542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/usstock/c/2021-03-01/doc-ikftpnnz0347473.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n該行計劃撤出香港、盧森堡和匈牙利等市場，這是其此前宣布的重組計劃的一部分。<br />\n巴塞羅那、布拉迪斯拉发和布魯塞爾等城市的分行也將關閉。<br />\n在阿塞拜疆、格魯吉亞、印度尼西亞、伊拉克、哈薩克斯坦、黎巴嫩、馬來西亞、<br />\n塞爾維亞和委內瑞拉的代表處也將於2024年關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bw9Iv6FLQZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dbw9Iv6FLQZQ&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=8fbebf0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bw9Iv6FLQZQ</a><br />\n<br />\nremarks:<br />\n走得好走."}]}